headline: Guidehouse Delivers Workday Transformation for City of Garland
summary: Guidehouse, a global AI-led professional services firm, has announced the successful go-live of Workday Financial Management for the City of Garland, Texas, marking a major milestone in the city's digital modernization journey. The deployment enhances financial efficiency, strengthens data transparency, and streamlines workflows across departments.
